at me like that?

03:07.637 --> 03:08.569
Sorry. Let me
understand this.

03:08.638 --> 03:09.570
So if Sam
asked you out-

03:09.639 --> 03:10.606
Darcy! Shh!

03:10.673 --> 03:12.072
You would just say,
"No, Sam."

03:12.142 --> 03:13.575
What are you doing?
He works here!

03:13.643 --> 03:15.076
