came out here.

12:42.178 --> 12:44.112
Yeah. That's me.

12:44.180 --> 12:45.613
Can I help you?

12:45.681 --> 12:47.546
Don't you think that's,
uh, kind of strange

12:47.616 --> 12:49.311
