13:04.767 --> 13:06.098
Do you do this
for a living?

13:06.168 --> 13:07.601
Videotape weddings?
Yeah.

13:07.670 --> 13:09.069
Bar mitzvahs, too.

13:09.138 --> 13:11.072
But, uh, in this case
it's kind of strange

13:11.140 --> 13:13.074
