13:28.491 --> 13:32.427
Just have a great time.
Call me when you get back, and, um...

13:32.495 --> 13:35.931
Oh, and if you see
a really big gift,

13:35.998 --> 13:38.592
really expensive gift
with no card,

13:38.667 --> 13:40.100
it's mine.

13:40.169 --> 13:41.602
My gift to you.

13:41.670 --> 13:43.103
Okay. Um, that's all.

13:43.172 --> 13:46.608
So have a wonderful time,
and I'll see you when you get back.

13:46.675 --> 13:47.607
Bye.

13:51.180 --> 13:54.115
Okay. Can... Can you
cut it now?

13:54.183 --> 13:57.751
Cut it.

13:57.820 --> 13:58.752
What?

13:58.821 --> 13:59.753
Cut it.

13:59.822 --> 14:00.811
Oh. I'm sorry.

14:00.890 --> 14:02.050
You've done
this before, huh?

14:02.124 --> 14:03.056
Oh, yeah.

14:06.495 --> 14:08.053
Whoo!

14:08.130 --> 14:09.563
Well, so, uh, I gotta
get back inside.

14:09.632 --> 14:11.566
